A COVERED EVENT (OCCURRING OVER SEVERAL DAYS) ANYWHERE IN THE UNITED STATES, CANADA, THE CARIBBEAN AND MEXICO AND WATERS CONTIGUOUS THERETO MAY BE USED TO SATISFY THE RETENTION. RECOVERIES UNDER THE

CATASTROPHE BONDS (IF ANY) WOULD BE FIRST APPLIED TO REDUCE LOSSES SUBJECT TO THIS TREATY.

