EXCESS OF $100 MILLION. THE TREATY COVERS AGGREGATE QUALIFYING LOSSES DURING 2014 FOR 40% OF $1.0 BILLION IN EXCESS OF $1.5 BILLION. THE TREATY COVERS ALL OF THE COMPANY'S

