TABLE OF CONTENTS

LOWER

THAN IN 2011. RENEWAL PREMIUM CHANGES REMAINED POSITIVE IN 2012 AND WERE HIGHER THAN IN 2011, PRIMARILY DUE TO RENEWAL RATE INCREASES. NEW BUSINESS PREMIUMS IN 2012 INCREASED OVER 2011.

SPECIALIZED DISTRIBUTION.

NET WRITTEN PREMIUMS OF $858 MILLION IN 2013 DECLINED BY 1% FROM 2012, DRIVEN BY PREMIUM DECREASES IN

