NATIONAL PROGRAMS BUSINESS UNIT. BUSINESS RETENTION RATES IN 2012 REMAINED STRONG BUT WERE LOWER THAN IN 2011. RENEWAL PREMIUM CHANGES REMAINED POSITIVE IN 2012 AND WERE HIGHER THAN IN 2011, PRIMARILY

DUE TO RENEWAL RATE INCREASES. NEW BUSINESS PREMIUMS IN 2012 DECREASED FROM 2011.

