WORLDWIDE HEAD OF FINANCIAL PLANNING, ANALYSIS AND REPORTING AT CITIGROUP AND CHIEF FINANCIAL OFFICER FOR CITIGROUP'S GLOBAL CONSUMER EUROPE, MIDDLE EAST AND AFRICA UNIT BETWEEN APRIL 2000 AND MARCH

